duties_responsibilities.duty: Identify damaged products within the warehouse and separate, clean-up, and repack or repair if warranted.
Transport product returns for processing and stage recouped product for return to inventory.
Follow Food Safety and Quality Control (Q.C.) standards and operate equipment such as a pallet jack or forklift.
Attend all required company meetings and perform other assigned duties as needed.

education_certification.credential: High School diploma or General Education Development (GED) or equivalent
